Package ru.ifmo.se.commands

Interface Executable

All Known Implementing Classes:
AddCommand, AddIfMaxCommand, ClearCommand, Command, CountByGenreCommand, ExecuteScriptCommand, ExitCommand, FilterLessThanNumberOfParticipantsCommand, FilterStartsWithNameCommand, HelpCommand, InfoCommand, RemoveAtIndexCommand, RemoveByIdCommand, RemoveLastCommand, SaveCommand, ShowCommand, UpdateByIdCommand
public interface Executable
Interface for executable commands in the application. Classes that implement this interface can be executed with an IOManager and arguments.

  • Method Details

    • execute

      boolean execute(IOManager ioManager, String[] arguments) throws IOException, WrongAmountOfArguments, WrongInputException
      Executes the command with the specified IO manager and arguments.
      Parameters:
      ioManager - the IO manager to use for input/output operations
      arguments - the arguments to pass to the command
      Returns:
      true if the command was executed successfully, false otherwise
      Throws:
      IOException - if an I/O error occurs
      WrongAmountOfArguments - if the number of arguments is incorrect
      WrongInputException - if the input is invalid
